item.title: CVE-2021-21551|2024-09-16T22:45:10.740Z -- dell -- dbutil
item.description: Dell dbutil_2_3.sys driver contains an insufficient access control vulnerability which may lead to escalation of privileges, denial of service, or information disclosure. Local authenticated user access is required.
